xim tun t-xi´n t-xmoxin tzalu. Myia, b´alo, b´a´n ela toj twitz tun t-xi t-xupin tib´aj
aju tx´otx´ q´aq´ ex kyuw, noqtzun tu´nj, toj juntl plaj, myia jun xjal n-chi ka´yin
te, n-chi ky-tx´u´n ky-tzi´ nimxix ky-q´ob´ extzen mya b´i´n t-xi tb´i´n tqanil, moqa
