twitz tkab´in t-xaq. . . . ¿Mintiʼpe in bʼant jun tiʼ tuʼna aju in nokx tqʼoʼna
n-chi tzaj ky-q´o´n ky-b´inchb´en Muggle ky-jay extzen n-chi b´aj ky-b´inchen?
