maske n-chi jyon kyi´j qa mya b´a´n tu´n ky-ok b´i´n. “N-chi jyone tun n-jyone
qa ma tz´etz lajo´na moqa mya. Kxel nq´o´ne jun u´j te Dumbledore
aj t-xi nq´o´ne teya, il ti´j tu´n tel tniky´ ti´j qa a Malfoy n-yolin tuk´e Fudge
ju majt."
