toj amb´il ja´lo — a, ikytzin tq´ama Dumbledore, mya nim q´uqb´il tk´u´j.
. . . B´a´n tu´n mi´n t-xi yolin ti´j jalin, Harry. . . .»
Aye ttzi ja n-chi jaqet extzen n-chi etz toj Atrium jalin ch´ixtoq t-xi´ t-xo´n. A Eric a xjal te xq´uqil n-chi kub´ tewin tib´aj t-xnaq´tzb´il Daily
Profeta juntl maj. Otoq che b´et t-xe t-xaq a´ te q´anpwaq na´mxtoq ttzaj tna´n Harry.
