CAPÍTULO
LUNA LOVEGOOD

A Harry tzaj jun nya b´a´n t-watl toj qonik´an. Aye tatey n-chi b´et ky-b´inchen extzen n-chi b´et
ti'j t-witzic', minti' in yolin; A qya Weasley tzaj oq´ ti´j
A t-xmilal Kreacher kyimni n-ka´yit tu´n Ron exttzen Hermione, aye n-chi ky-q´o´n ky-corona, extzen juntl maj a Harry n-ok tka´yin tib´ n-b´et toj jun corredor n-pon b´aj toj jun ttzi ja tz´apin. Jun rat naj jaw weʼ tukʼil t-xbʼalun
n-chi tzalaj tu´n t-xi tka´yin a Ron ya b´aj t-xb´alumin tib´ extzen n-yolin tuk´e.
