n-chi b´et t-xe´l toj b´e qlolj n-chi b´aj t-xmo´n jb´al ti´jxi Hogsmeade
xkotzb'il.
tzalu ate´qe jun syent moqa mas stagecoaches mya ky-chej extzen tkyaqil amb´il
xi kyi´n aye xnaq´tzanjtz te tnejel ab´q´i tzmax toj ja te kawb´il. Xi tka´yin Harry
jun rat naj kyi´j, n-chi el tpa´n tib´ tun t-xi tka´yin Ron exttzen
Hermione, yajxi´tl b´ant jun t-xilen.
Aye coches ya myia ky-chej. Attoq junjun txuk wa´l ky-xol t-xaq kar; noqwit il ti´j tu´n t-xi tq´o´n jun kyb´i, a
n-ximana qa n-chi tzaj tqona kye chej, maske at jun ti´x n-chi b´et kyi´j, ax ikx. Mintiʼtoq kychibʼjal, aju ky
q´eq t-xb´alun n-chi tzqij kyi´j ky-b´aqil, aye tkyaqil ky-b´aqil n-chi yek´unte. A ky-wi´ tzaj t-xilen jun dragón, extzen aye ky-witz mya t-xnaq´tzb´en saq extzen
n-ka´yin. Aye t-xik´ n-chi etz toj junjun t-xu´k — nimxix, q´eq ky-chik´
ky-xik´ aye t-xik´ n-chi ky-ka´yin tze´nku kye ky-xik´ aye nimxix ky-chik´.
In che kubʼ weʼ ex mintiʼ in che yolin toj qlolj, aʼyeju txkup in che keʼyintoq nya bʼaʼn ex
nya b´a´n. A Harry mya b´i´n t-xnaq´tzan tiqu´n n-chi b´et aye entrenadores
n-chi tzaj ky-q´i´n aye chej nya b´a´n lu tej t-xi´ ky-b´inchen
n-chi b´et kyjunalx.
¿Jatum ta´ tx´yan? chi Ron tq´ajq´ajel twi´, ttxlaj Harry.
